# File Size and Splitting

- Keep files under 300 lines whenever possible.
- If a file grows too large, split by responsibility before adding more logic.
- Extract reusable UI into components and non-UI logic into services/utilities.
- Break large templates into smaller components.
- Prefer small focused units over large multi-purpose files.

## Split Triggers

- Multiple independent sections in one component.
- Large computed/state blocks with unrelated concerns.
- Repeated markup/styling patterns.
